com.esri.mo2.client.io
Class EsrimapSecureOutputStream

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.client.io.EsrimapSecureOutputStream
public class EsrimapSecureOutputStream
extends Object

This class implements methods to send authenticated requests to the Administrator in the Application Server. The stream can be accessed just like a standard java I/O stream, but you must ensure to call Login before a request (using one or more write calls) is made.
